THANK YOU for the most wonderful INKtober! What a delicious month of illustrations. Slide to see our GIVEAWAY! We are giving away 24 of our 2021 They Draw & Cook Calendars published by @amberlotuspublishing ✨ Leave a comment telling us your fave autumn food. We will randomly choose 24 winners on November 4th. All winners will be announced here on this post. Huge thanks to everyone who participated in #inktoberwithtdac and to all of you who followed along and cheered us on!  Cover art by @catherinepaiano
